title: Gensou Suikoden I - Category (Doujinshi)
description: When an old neighbor comes to visit, McDohl hesitates over how to introduce Ted. What exactly is Ted to him? A "friend', a "family member", or more like a "brother"? This thoughtful doujinshi deals with how people categorize other people and focuses on McDohl & Ted in one part and Cleo and Gremio in the next.
